otice There is no textbook for dealing with teenage sporting stardom, but Maisie Summers-Newton is as qualified as anyone to write it.\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 518, \"end\": 539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maisie_Summers-Newton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maisie Summers-Newton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maisie_Summers-Newton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maisie_Summers-Newton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 431, \"to\": 448}, {\"ngram\": \"no textbook\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 469}, {\"ngram\": \"teenage sporting stardom\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 511}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The swimmer was thrust into the spotlight as a 19-year-old just as her idol Ellie Simmonds was leaving it, making for an awkward dynamic as she won gold in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 656, \"end\": 670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellie_Simmonds\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ellie Simmonds\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellie_Simmonds\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellie_Simmonds\"}, {\"begin\": 736, \"end\": 741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9892694274973672, \"rank\": 0.01084640261135512, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The swimmer\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 591}, {\"ngram\": \"the spotlight\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 621}, {\"ngram\": \"her idol\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 655}, {\"ngram\": \"an awkward dynamic\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 716}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now 22, she has spent the last three years stewing on the defence of her 200m individual medley title, all while becoming the face of British para swimming.\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 878, \"end\": 885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9734652772492836, \"rank\": 0.018525988379472638, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last three years\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 786}, {\"ngram\": \"the defence\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 809}, {\"ngram\": \"her 200m individual medley title\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 845}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have a lot of self-doubt,\\\" said Summers-Newton, who is one of over 1,000 elite athletes on UK Sport's National Lottery-funded World Class Programme, allowing them to train full time, have access to the world's best coaches and benefit from pioneering medical support - which has been vital on their pathway to the Paris 2024 Games.\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 1236, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 996, \"end\": 1004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 996, \"end\": 1004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 915}, {\"ngram\": \"Summers-Newton\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"over 1,000 elite athletes\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1099}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's best coaches\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1127}, {\"ngram\": \"medical support\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"their pathway\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Games\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think that's something that has come since Tokyo, there is a lot of pressure being Paralympic champion and then defending it.\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1366, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1284, \"end\": 1289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9892694274973672, \"rank\": 0.01084640261135512, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1305}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1317}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympic champion\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just put so much pressure on myself.\\\"\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1406, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so much pressure\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At least to those in the stands at La Defense Arena, Summers-Newton need not have worried.\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1498, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the stands\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1439}, {\"ngram\": \"La Defense Arena\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1459}, {\"ngram\": \"Summers-Newton\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1475}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was behind after the butterfly and backstroke legs but that was all part of the plan as she used her breaststroke strength to surge clear and claim victory by 5.60 seconds.\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1676, \"entities\": [], \"noun_