1972, \"to\": 1986}, {\"ngram\": \"those three years\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2014}, {\"ngram\": \"her self-worth\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2038}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2058}, {\"ngram\": \"a shining example\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2077}, {\"ngram\": \"a generation\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2094}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2117}, {\"ngram\": \"elite sport\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has qualified as a teacher and finished her last placement at Bridgewater Primary School in March.\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2237, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2201, \"end\": 2212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earl_of_Bridgewater\", \"score\": 0.906134403354934, \"rank\": 0.10358904395219433, \"text\": \"Bridgewater\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earl_of_Bridgewater\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earl_of_Bridgewater\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a teacher\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2165}, {\"ngram\": \"her last placement\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2197}, {\"ngram\": \"March\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That is something I really had to work hard for,\\\" said Summers-Newton.\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2310, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2257}, {\"ngram\": \"Summers-Newton\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2309}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Swimming comes naturally but writing assignments, going into schools, and teaching for eight weeks, it was tough, and I made some incredible memories.\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2462, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Swimming\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2320}, {\"ngram\": \"assignments\", \"from\": 2349, \"to\": 2360}, {\"ngram\": \"schools\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2380}, {\"ngram\": \"eight weeks\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2410}, {\"ngram\": \"some incredible memories\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2461}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it's allowed me to have a side of me where I do not have to think about swimming 24 hours a day.\\\"\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2570, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a side\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2503}, {\"ngram\": \"24 hours\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Summers-Newton has blossomed into the ringleader of the British squad and is directing traffic in the seven-strong flat of female swimmers in the Paralympic Village.\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2628, \"end\": 2635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9734652772492836, \"rank\": 0.018525988379472638, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2718, \"end\": 2736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paralympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Summers-Newton\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2586}, {\"ngram\": \"the ringleader\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2620}, {\"ngram\": \"traffic\", \"from\": 2659, \"to\": 2666}, {\"ngram\": \"the seven-strong flat\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2691}, {\"ngram\": \"female swimmers\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are all so close, my girls, and it's the best flat ever,\\\" said Summers-Newton.\", \"from\": 2739, \"to\": 2821, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Summers-Newton\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2820}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have definitely become a more senior member of the team.\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2881, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a more senior member\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2868}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2880}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have got such young athletes like Poppy [Maskill] and Iona [Winnifrith] coming up and for me, it's about trying to inspire them and pass on as much knowledge as I can.\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 3054, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such young athletes\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 2915}, {\"ngram\": \"Poppy\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 2926}, {\"ngram\": \"Iona\", \"from\": 2941, \"to\": 2945}, {\"ngram\": \"as much knowledge\", \"from\": 3027, \"to\": 3044}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It comes quite naturally to me, and I'd like to think I am quite a caring, motherly type of person.\\\"\", \"from\": 3056, \"to\": 3157, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"quite a caring, motherly type\", \"from\": 3116, \"to\": 3145}, {\"ngram\": \"person\", \"from\": 3149, \"to\": 3155}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maskill, Winnifrith and company could wish for no better role model when it comes to coping with pressure.\", \"from\": 3159, \"to\": 3265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Maskill\", \"from\": 3159, \"to\": 3166}, {\"ngram\": \"Winnifrith\", \"from\": 3168, \"to\": 3178}, {\"ngram\": \"company\", \"from\": 3183, \"to\": 3190}, {\"ngram\": \"no better role model\", \"from\": 3206, \"to\": 3226}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 3256, \"to\": 3264}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Summers-Newton has another title to defend in the 100m breaststroke, but the British squad will not benefit from her leadership indefinitely.\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3344, \"end\": 3351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9734652772492836, \"rank\": 0.018525988379472638, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Summers\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3274}, {\"ngram\": \"Newton\", \"from\": 3275, \"to\": 3281}, {\"ngram\": \"another title\", \"from\": 3286, \"to\": 3299}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m breaststroke\", \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3334}, {\"ngram\": \"her leadership\", \"from\": 3380, \"to\": 3394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At some point soon, she will swap the pool for the classroom and set about changing another set of lives.\", \"from\": 3410, \"to\": 3515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some point\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3423}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 3444, \"to\": 3452}, {\"ngram\": \"the classroom\", \"from\": 3457, \"to\": 3470}, {\"ngram\": \"another set\", \"from\": 3494, \"to\": 3505}, {\"ngram\": \"lives\", \"from\": 3509, \"to\": 3514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can hopefully get a little bit faster,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3569, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I definitely think I will have a rest after this Games and we will see what happens after that in terms of swimming, but I am only 22 so hopefully a lot more can come.\\\"\", \"from\": 3570, \"to\": 3739, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a rest\", \"from\": 3602, \"to\": 3608}, {\"ngram\": \"this Games\", \"from\": 3615, \"to\": 3625}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 3669, \"to\": 3674}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 3678, \"to\": 3686}]}, {\"sentence\": \"National Lottery players raise more than \\u00a330million a week for Good Causes including vital funding into sport - from grassroots to elite.\", \"from\": 3741, \"to\": 3878, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3741, \"end\": 3757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"score\": 0.9999999841506907, \"rank\": 1.5849237313471556e-08, \"text\": \"National Lottery\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Good Causes\", \"fro